[..] collisions
[..] network halts
[..] slowdowns
1) upgrade net tools for the misprint of collisions and
2) upgrade the tulip.c driver for the rest.
the stock tulip.c driver in the kernel is broken.  you can grab a new
version of it from 
ftp://cesdis.gsfc.nasa.gov/pub/linux/drivers/
try version .90q
